---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import airbnbImage from "@/assets/imgs/airbnb.png";
import financialImage from "@/assets/imgs/financial.png";
import tripadvisorImage from "@/assets/imgs/tripadvisor.png";
import cnbcImage from "@/assets/imgs/cnbc.png";
import wolrd_travel_awardsImage from "@/assets/imgs/wolrd_travel_awards.png";
import global_wellnessImage from "@/assets/imgs/global_wellness.png";
---

<section
  class="container invest_section flex flex-col text-center pt-8 px-4 lg:px-11 xl:px-36 min-[1536px]:px-72 text-xs md:text-sm"
>
  <div>
    <div>
      <div class="font-title uppercase text-2xl md:text-6xl">
        <h1>Why invest in Tulum?</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-10 pb-10 md:px-28">
        <p>
          Government initiatives like the <b
            >Tulum International Airport, Mayan Train, and Jaguar Park are
            expected to increase the flow of tourism in Tulum</b
          >, with the new airport anticipated to attract over <b
            >5 million new visitors</b
          > annually.<br />
          The expansion of global companies into Tulum underscores <b
            >confidence in the market</b
          >, while the potential influx of tourists from India, Japan, and China
          further enhances this promising outlook.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="pt-0 pb-10">
        <div
          class="border-2 border-accent-700 text-accent-700 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 p-10 gap-y-0 md:gap-x-4"
        >
          <div>
            <div class="font-subtitle text-xl p-4">
              <h2>#1 Ranking</h2>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>Tourist destination in Mexico.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-subtitle text-xl p-4">
              <h2>6.5+ million</h2>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>Tourists per year (#1 hotspot in all Latin America).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-subtitle text-xl p-4">
              <h2>$7.1+ Billion</h2>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>Yearly spent by tourists ($1,000+ avg. per visitor).</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="font-subtitle text-xl pt-4 pb-4">
              <h2>87% of tourists</h2>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>Are foreigners with high purchase power.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="pb-10 md:px-28">
        <p>
          With the recent announcement of the government infrastructure program,
          Cenote Gardens is not just about sustainable luxury living; it is a
          savvy investment in a tangible asset poised for appreciation.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="font-title uppercase pb-10 text-2xl">
        <h2>Tulum industry awards & media recognitions</h2>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-6">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center pb-8">
        <Image
          class="invest__airbnbImage max-w-20 md:max-w-32"
          src={airbnbImage}
          alt="Airbnb Image"
        />
        <p>
          “Destination with the 4th most reservations globally for New Years.”
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center pb-8">
        <Image
          class="invest__financialImage max-w-20 md:max-w-32"
          src={financialImage}
          alt="Financial Image"
        />
        <p>“One of the markets with the most growth in the world.”</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center pb-8">
        <Image
          class="invest__tripadvisorImage max-w-20 md:max-w-32"
          src={tripadvisorImage}
          alt="Tripadvisor Image"
        />
        <p>“Best up and coming travel destination in the world.”</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center pb-8">
        <Image
          class="invest__cnbcImage max-w-20 md:max-w-32"
          src={cnbcImage}
          alt="Cnbc Image"
        />
        <p>“Most tourist destination in the planet.”</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center pb-8">
        <Image
          class="invest__wolrd_travel_awardsImage max-w-20 md:max-w-32"
          src={wolrd_travel_awardsImage}
          alt="Wolrd_travel_awards Image"
        />
        <p>“Leading beach destination in Mexico and Central America.”</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center pb-8">
        <Image
          class="invest__global_wellnessImage max-w-20 md:max-w-32"
          src={global_wellnessImage}
          alt="Global_wellness Image"
        />
        <p>“Tulum is the global capital of yoga”</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
